description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you an outstanding nurse ready for your next challenge? Do you share our Trust values and strive for clinical excellence? Would you like to work in an outstanding Trust and make a difference to people’s lives?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At UHBW, our nurses truly are the life blood of our Trust and we pride ourselves on creating a nurturing environment for our nursing staff to take the next step in their nursing journey. You may be ready for a change from your current specialty or it may be that you are at a point in your career where you&#39;ve got some itchy feet and just want a new environment. Whatever the case let us show you that UHBW is the place for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please state in your application your preferred specialty and your availability to work in Bristol and Weston.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for nurses who inspire others and who work harder because they want to, not because they have to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At UHBW, we’ll give you the tools and support but you will be in full control of your development. Our nurses know why they chose to continue their nursing journey here, join us and find out your reason why.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nursingrercruitment@UHBW.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
